
┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│  CUSTOMER (Frontend/Client)         │  ← Orders food
│  "I want a burger"                  │
└──────────────┬──────────────────────┘
               │
┌──────────────▼──────────────────────┐
│  WAITER (Controller Layer)          │  ← Takes orders, serves food
│  - Takes customer's order           │
│  - Brings food to customer          │
└──────────────┬──────────────────────┘
               │
┌──────────────▼──────────────────────┐
│  CHEF (Service Layer)               │  ← Prepares the food
│  - Knows recipes                    │
│  - Makes business decisions         │
│  - Combines ingredients             │
└──────────────┬──────────────────────┘
               │
┌──────────────▼──────────────────────┐
│  STORAGE (Repository Layer)         │  ← Gets ingredients
│  - Fetches from fridge/pantry       │
│  - Stores leftovers                 │
└──────────────┬──────────────────────┘
               │
┌──────────────▼──────────────────────┐
│  PANTRY (Database)                  │  ← Where everything is stored
│  - Raw ingredients stored here      │
└─────────────────────────────────────┘
